Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右
